INSTALL
	- Create database ticket_db and execute ticket_db.sql
	- Update MTC_CLASS with the DB connection, STORE URL, STORE ID, SECRET KEY
	- Style Index.php

OPTIONAL
	It's preferable to set debug to true in production enviroment